nited_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 621, \"end\": 626, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999850660971, \"rank\": 1.4933833537690857e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his fifth Olympic medal\", \"from\": 552, \"to\": 575}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 587}, {\"ngram\": \"the 10m synchronised event\", \"from\": 591, \"to\": 617}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I felt so incredibly nervous going into this, knowing it was my last Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my last Olympics\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 752}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was a lot of pressure and expectations.\", \"from\": 756, \"to\": 802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 776, \"to\": 784}, {\"ngram\": \"expectations\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was eager for it to be done.\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 833, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But when I walked out and saw my husband (Lance) and kids (Robbie and Phoenix) and my friends and family in the audience, I was like, you know what?\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 893, \"end\": 899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.882343601274457, \"rank\": 0.07967065666975813, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\"}, {\"begin\": 904, \"end\": 911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.9964933256285219, \"rank\": 0.003462926156975691, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \